# Focalboard Android App - Build Progress

## Completed Tasks

### 1. Basic App Structure ✅
- Created `FocalboardApp.kt` - Application class with notification channel setup
- Created `MainActivity.kt` - Entry point with Compose setup and navigation
- Configured `AndroidManifest.xml` with required permissions (INTERNET, ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE)
- Set up Material 3 theme with `Theme.kt`

### 2. Navigation Setup ✅
- Created `NavGraph.kt` with navigation routes:
  - Login screen (start destination)
  - Main screen (board list)
  - Board detail screen (placeholder for future implementation)
- Implemented navigation between screens with proper back stack handling

### 3. Focalboard API Client ✅
- Created `ApiService.kt` with:
  - OkHttp client with custom CookieJar for CSRF token handling
  - X-Requested-With header interceptor for API requests
  - HTTP logging interceptor for debugging
  - 30-second timeouts for connect/read/write
- Created `FocalboardApi.kt` interface with:
  - `getCsrfToken()` - Get CSRF token from server
  - `login()` - Authenticate with email/password
  - `getCurrentUser()` - Get current user info
  - `getBoards()` - Get all boards
  - `getBoard()` - Get specific board by ID
  - `createBoard()` - Create new board
  - `getBoardViews()` - Get board views (layouts)
  - `getBoardRows()` - Get rows (cards) for a view
  - `createRow()`, `updateRow()`, `deleteRow()` - Card operations
- Defined data models: `LoginRequestV2`, `AuthResponseV2`, `UserInfo`, `Board`, `BoardView`, `BoardRow`, etc.

### 4. Authentication ✅
- Created `SettingsManager.kt` with DataStore for persistent storage:
  - Server URL storage
  - Auth token storage
  - User info storage (id, email, username, display name)
  - `clearAuth()` for logout
- Created `AuthRepository.kt` with:
  - `login()` - Handles CSRF token retrieval and authentication
  - `logout()` - Clears stored credentials
  - `isLoggedIn` property to check authentication status
  - Flow-based accessors for reactive data access
- Created `LoginScreen.kt` with:
  - Server URL input field
  - Username/Email input field
  - Password input field (with visual transformation)
  - Loading state with progress indicator
  - Error handling with error display
  - Connection button with validation

### 5. Board List View ✅
- Created Room database for local caching:
  - `BoardEntity.kt` - Entity for board data
  - `BoardDao.kt` - Data Access Object with queries
  - `FocalboardDatabase.kt` - Room database setup
- Created `BoardRepository.kt` with:
  - `getBoards()` - Flow-based board retrieval from local DB
  - `refreshBoards()` - Fetch from server and cache locally
  - `getBoardById()` - Get single board
  - `clearCachedBoards()` - Clear cache for a server
- Created `MainViewModel.kt` with:
  - `MainUiState` sealed class for UI states (Loading, Success, Error, NotAuthenticated)
  - State management with `StateFlow`
  - `refreshBoards()` - Trigger board refresh
  - `logout()` - Handle logout
  - Automatic board observation and state updates
- Created `MainScreen.kt` with:
  - `BoardList` - LazyColumn of board cards
  - `BoardItem` - Individual board card with name, description, icon
  - `EmptyState` - Shown when no boards exist
  - `ErrorState` - Shown on error with retry option
  - `ErrorBanner` - Inline error notification
  - `LogoutDialog` - Confirmation dialog for logout
  - Top app bar with refresh and logout buttons
  - Floating action button for creating new board
  - Loading indicator during refresh
- Updated `build.gradle.kts` with:
  - KSP plugin for Room annotation processing
  - lifecycle-viewmodel-compose dependency

## Project Structure

```
app/src/main/kotlin/com/focalboard/android/
├── FocalboardApp.kt           # Application class
├── MainActivity.kt             # Entry point
├── data/
│   ├── api/
│   │   ├── ApiService.kt      # Retrofit/OkHttp setup
│   │   └── FocalboardApi.kt   # API interface
│   ├── local/
│   │   ├── SettingsManager.kt # DataStore for preferences
│   │   ├── BoardEntity.kt     # Room entity
│   │   ├── BoardDao.kt        # Room DAO
│   │   └── FocalboardDatabase.kt # Room database
│   └── repository/
│       ├── AuthRepository.kt  # Authentication logic
│       └── BoardRepository.kt # Board data access
└── ui/
    ├── navigation/
    │   └── NavGraph.kt         # Navigation setup
    ├── screens/
    │   ├── login/
    │   │   └── LoginScreen.kt  # Login UI
    │   └── main/
    │       └── MainScreen.kt   # Board list UI
    ├── theme/
    │   └── Theme.kt            # Material 3 theme
    └── viewmodel/
        └── MainViewModel.kt    # Main screen ViewModel
```

## Dependencies

- **Retrofit 2.9.0** - REST API client
- **OkHttp 4.12.0** - HTTP client with logging interceptor
- **Room 2.6.1** - Local database for caching
- **DataStore Preferences 1.0.0** - Settings storage
- **Navigation Compose 2.7.5** - In-app navigation
- **Jetpack Compose 1.6.1** - UI toolkit
- **Material 3 1.2.0** - Design system
- **Kotlin Coroutines 1.7.3** - Async programming

## Next Steps (Future Enhancements)

1. Board detail screen with cards/rows view
2. Create board functionality
3. Create/edit/delete cards
4. Multiple view types (grid, kanban, gallery)
5. Card properties and columns
6. Offline sync improvements
7. Push notifications

